                <head>250. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>Secretary of State <persName corresp="#p_DAW1">Dulles</persName> left Paris on
                    May 6, 1957. The Ambassadors continued their discussions until May 8, but no
                    record of their meetings has been found in Department of State files.</p>
            </div>
